dct_title_s: [Kharitat al-Iraq]: nahiyata Shahraban wa Mahrut wa Shubat Ba'qubah
dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat al-Masahah al-Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Surveys. [[Map of Iraq]: Shahraban and Mahrut districts, Ba'qubah section]. Alternate title: liwa' Diyali: qada' Ba'qubah: nahiyata Shahraban wa Mahrut wa shu'bat Ba'qubah. [Dayali province: Ba'qubah district: Sharaban and Mahrut section, with Ba'gubah division.] Relief shown by hachures and form lines. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1924, 1925, 1926, 1927. Tribal lands and ownership are shown.
